node.text:
Happy Daiquiri Day
.
The Lovers Daiquiri
.
When David Cordoba creates rum with daiquiri in mind you can expect something exciting
.
 The Lovers Daiquiri ( Perfect Daiquiri )
.
60 ml The Lovers Rum
30 ml Fresh Lime Juice
2  tsps Sugar (preferably from Sugar Cane)
.
Method: 
Place all ingredients into a cocktail shaker
Stir well until the sugar has dissolved
Fill shaker with cubed and crushed ice (half/half)
Shake  until the shaker is frozen.
Double strain into a pre-chilled glass.
.
PS “Never use lemon juice. And Remember please, that a too sweet Daiquiri is like a lovely lady with too much perfume” –
.
Charles H. Baker Jr.
.
